OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy light rain at first
OL,6,Fthrough the Trossachs and the west.
OL,7,FOtherwise it will be dry with some
OL,8,Fvariable cloud cover and some bright
OL,9,For sunny spells. Feeling warm in any
OL,10,Fafternoon sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,13,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,14,Fdry across all parts with variable
OL,15,Famounts of cloud and clear periods.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAfter a dry morning rain
OL,18,Fwill spread southeast during the
OL,19,Fafternoon. Mild in the morning but
OL,20,Fturning colder during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
