OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Ffor most of Thursday but patchy rain
OL,7,Fspreading east later. Unsettled with
OL,8,Fshowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,9,FFriday and Saturday.
